name: Wizardry hunting.Start
description: This work is a continuation of my graphic series Silent Hunting, which I have been working on since 2020.The work is devoted to the ecology and conservation of forests,this is a fantasy about the nature of the future.The night is the time when the forest can be seen in all its glory. Whirlwinds rage between its stems, battles are played out,a new world is being created. 8192x4920 px, JPG, 5,57 MB
